      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>tofu</strong> into strips</p><p>Add the <strong>tofu strips</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
