    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber </strong>in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them finely, discard the stalks</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped coriander </strong>and <strong>chopped mint</strong>,<strong> </strong>then finely chop them together</p>",
