    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> grated carrot</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber </strong>and <strong>cider vinegar </strong>to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled carrot & cucumber salad</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
