        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>mayo </strong>in a bowl with a splash of <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>harissa dressing</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>cooked brown rice</strong> with the <strong>chopped coriander & mint </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>herby rice</strong></p>",
