    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>herby rice</strong> with the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>crispy smoky tofu</strong> and the <strong>quick-pickled carrot & cucumber salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>harissa dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
